  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Unrefined Catalytic Element",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "未提炼催化元素",
    "TencentChinese": "未提炼催化元素",
    "TraditionalChinese": "未精製催化元素"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">catalyst</span>, useful for charging <span class=\"name name-commodity\">defensive technologies</span> such as shields or hazard protection.<br> <br>Exosuit material handling technology allows automatic harvesting from appropriate <CATALYST<>sodium-rich flora<>.<br><br>A vital ingredient in the creation of many advanced devices, products and components.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种强大的<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">催化剂</span>，用于为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御技术</span>（如护盾和危险防护）充能。<br> <br>套装的材料处理技术使其能在合适的<CATALYST<>富钠植物群系<>中自动收获。<br><br>这是制作很多高级设备、产品和部件的关键原料。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种强大的<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">催化剂</span>，用于为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御技术</span>（如护盾和危险防护）充能。<br> <br>套装的材料处理技术使其能在合适的<CATALYST<>富钠植物群系<>中自动收获。<br><br>这是制作很多高级设备、产品和部件的关键原料。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種強力<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">催化劑</span>，能用來為防護罩或風險防護系統等<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防衛科技</span>充能。<br> <br>強化套裝上的材料處理科技，遇到適當的<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">富鈉植物</span>時，會自動採集鈉。<br><br>製作許多先進裝置、產品與元件時都少不了這項原料。"
  },
